title: Camp WeWow Bug Week Day 4
description:
It's Weather Week at Camp WeWow! Today, we're playing a round of Two Whats and A Wow!! Visit tinkercast.com/resource/game-two-whats-and-a-wow-the-bug-edition for directions to today's activity and share what you're tinkering with at tinkercast.com/share!
